title: Camp WeWow Music Week Day 2
description:
It's Music Week at Camp WeWow! Today, we're building our own musical instruments!! Visit tinkercast.com/resource/craft-build-your-own-instruments for directions to today's activity and share what you're tinkering with at tinkercast.com/share! Do you know an item that isn’t an instrument but you think should be?! Call us at 1-888-7WOW-WOW to share! You just might get featured around the Camp WeWow Campfire this Friday!

See Privacy Policy at https://art19.com/privacy and California Privacy Notice at https://art19.com/privacy#do-not-sell-my-info.
